I am a lv 39 druid and I recently aquired a manastone. I am looking for advice on how and where I can use it to its full effectiveness. Should I just regen myself and then use it periodically. I have heard something about binding in kunark/Vel, port out, click manastone till full mana and gate back tactic? I appreciate any info you can give. Thanks in Advance =)<br>
